Encounter.Name: Rival Arrival
Encounter.Notes: If they outnumber the PC's, they'll try to isolate and capture individuals for use as leverage. They flee if half their number are incapacitated, but return later unless the Imperials arrive. If half are killed, they give up Cholganna.[P] This encounter sheet can also be used for the [B]Imperials Attack[b] encounter.

ItemDescInfo.MiscDesc: Blocks sensors within range, counting the ship's silhouette as one smaller when being fired upon.
Immediately notifies all ships in a star system or within 100 kilometers if planetside to the ship or vehicle's existence.
